Dragon claws, 4 hits.
No fucking shitty custom items. [/b] No antileech cause I want the noobs to leech it, the base was ChosenPkz. Thanks for it. =) I might add a antileech..But for now leech it... Alot more features, just cant be fucked to add pictures and write crap about it.
